Tip for Multi-Module Projects with Maven Release Plugin

I am particularly interested in multi-module projects. Therefore, I extended the example
from Section 10: Multi-Module Projects with Maven Release Plugin. Initially, I encountered
the issue that no deployment was found in the nexus-release repository. On subsequent attempts,
I received error messages from GitHub stating "tag already exists."

Solution:
Using <revision> (and references to it like ${project.version} and ${revision})
with the Maven Release Plugin is not possible. However, the Maven Release Plugin
manages this task itself, making it unnecessary to use <revision>.
